						"cell_type": "markdown",
						"metadata": {
							"nteract": {
								"transient": {
									"deleting": false
								}
							}
						},
						"source": [
							"Although printing the secret also shows the string 'REDACTED' as in Databricks, the 'hack' to show the password by printing letter by letter is also present in synapse."
						]
					},
					{
						"cell_type": "code",
